      "description": "IPIP representation of the VIA character strength 'Spirituality/Religiousness'. 9-item subscale from the full IPIP-VIA inventory. Each item is rated on a 5-point accuracy scale. Part of the Values in Action framework (Peterson & Seligman, 2004).",
      "citation": "Peterson, C., & Seligman, M. E. P. (2004). Character Strengths and Virtues: A Handbook and Classification. Oxford University Press. IPIP items: Goldberg et al. (2006). https://ipip.ori.org/newVIAKey.htm",
